<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BCSO - Maintenance</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #07090e;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1510 0%, #07090e 100%);
        }
        .maintenance-box {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 20px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.4));
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #bda581;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .loader {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #bda581;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 10px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.2)); }
            50% { filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 30px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.6)); }
            100% { filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 10px rgba(189, 165, 129, 0.2)); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-box">
        <img src="/images/bcso.png" alt="BCSO Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Réseau Sécurisé Inaccessible</h1>
        <p>Le système informatique du Blaine County Sheriff's Office est actuellement en cours de maintenance. Nos techniciens procèdent à une mise à niveau des serveurs.</p>
        <p>Veuillez réessayer plus tard.</p>
        <div class="loader">
            <i class="fas fa-cog fa-spin"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>